fulltitle: Rob Interviews the renowned  Cab Calloway.    1990

description: I had the pleasure of sitting in a little cafe having a chat with the Renowned Cab Calloway back in Aug 1990 while on a Church Choir Tour in Muskegon MI.     Cab was a little faded but took the time to discuss football with my Brother in Law.    For those who don't know Cab Calloways work, I've placed some vintage footage at the end of this clip.   He was like the Black Fred Astaire of the early 1900's
